{"id": "ZH_B00007_S00000_W000000", "wav": "ZH_B00007/ZH_B00007_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00007_S00000_W000000.mp3", "text": "资本主义民主国家如何拖延危机？", "duration": 3.344, "speaker": "ZH_B00007_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.0161}
{"id": "ZH_B00007_S00000_W000001", "wav": "ZH_B00007/ZH_B00007_S00000/mp3/ZH_B00007_S00000_W000001.mp3", "text": "威特曼直到前不久，还一直是联邦总理默克尔最重要的经济智囊团成员。", "duration": 5.993, "speaker": "ZH_B00007_S00000", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2803}
