{"id": "ZH_B00007_S00002_W000032", "wav": "ZH_B00007/ZH_B00007_S00002/mp3/ZH_B00007_S00002_W000032.mp3", "text": "如经济学家提出的工人消极怠工的理论所说，为什么资方。", "duration": 5.824, "speaker": "ZH_B00007_S00002", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3178}
{"id": "ZH_B00007_S00002_W000033", "wav": "ZH_B00007/ZH_B00007_S00002/mp3/ZH_B00007_S00002_W000033.mp3", "text": "为什么劳方在资方眼中总是会涉嫌逃避劳动？", "duration": 4.1775, "speaker": "ZH_B00007_S00002", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1967}
{"id": "ZH_B00007_S00002_W000034", "wav": "ZH_B00007/ZH_B00007_S00002/mp3/ZH_B00007_S00002_W000034.mp3", "text": "比如在这一地带中有着多样性的结果，依赖的获取报酬方式。", "duration": 6.078, "speaker": "ZH_B00007_S00002", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3194}
{"id": "ZH_B00007_S00002_W000035", "wav": "ZH_B00007/ZH_B00007_S00002/mp3/ZH_B00007_S00002_W000035.mp3", "text": "留给在工业生产部门手工劳动者的计件工资。", "duration": 4.754, "speaker": "ZH_B00007_S00002", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1792}
