{"id": "ZH_B00007_S00002_W000038", "wav": "ZH_B00007/ZH_B00007_S00002/mp3/ZH_B00007_S00002_W000038.mp3", "text": "问题的关键是要详细分析并区分。", "duration": 3.073, "speaker": "ZH_B00007_S00002", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.0182}
{"id": "ZH_B00007_S00002_W000039", "wav": "ZH_B00007/ZH_B00007_S00002/mp3/ZH_B00007_S00002_W000039.mp3", "text": "是不设上限的追求收益最大化的资本积累。", "duration": 3.956, "speaker": "ZH_B00007_S00002", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.0891}
{"id": "ZH_B00007_S00002_W000040", "wav": "ZH_B00007/ZH_B00007_S00002/mp3/ZH_B00007_S00002_W000040.mp3", "text": "还是传统上保障生存发展的既定或按一定标准增长的收入水平。", "duration": 7.216, "speaker": "ZH_B00007_S00002", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.2415}
{"id": "ZH_B00007_S00002_W000041", "wav": "ZH_B00007/ZH_B00007_S00002/mp3/ZH_B00007_S00002_W000041.mp3", "text": "两种经济模式在资本主义制度中并列作为不同的行动导向。", "duration": 5.654, "speaker": "ZH_B00007_S00002", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1826}
{"id": "ZH_B00007_S00002_W000042", "wav": "ZH_B00007/ZH_B00007_S00002/mp3/ZH_B00007_S00002_W000042.mp3", "text": "他们分别有有着互相冲突、有时互相渗透的需要和要求的不同。社会集团和社会机构所代表。", "duration": 10.119, "speaker": "ZH_B00007_S00002", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.0764}
{"id": "ZH_B00007_S00003_W000000", "wav": "ZH_B00007/ZH_B00007_S00003/mp3/ZH_B00007_S00003_W000000.mp3", "text": "把贝奥康纳和贝尔中新预言的现代国家的财政危机定位在收入而非支出方面。", "duration": 8.031, "speaker": "ZH_B00007_S00003", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.1207}
{"id": "ZH_B00007_S00003_W000001", "wav": "ZH_B00007/ZH_B00007_S00003/mp3/ZH_B00007_S00003_W000001.mp3", "text": "人们把这种危机定义成为一种歌德雪和熊彼特意义上的税收国家的危机。", "duration": 6.774, "speaker": "ZH_B00007_S00003", "language": "zh", "dnsmos": 3.3245}
